readable.content: A dock over water with a palm tree at the end and five boats , during twilight . A man stands on a dock near several boats , while 2 other men are on one of the boats . Boats docked at a pier which has three men and a lone palm tree . Boats parked at a marina at sunset . There are three people on the dock by the boats .
